# Smart Employee Platform

## Technical Design Document

---

# 1. Project Overview

The Smart Employee Platform is a serverless employee management and attendance solution built on AWS. The platform combines employee onboarding, leave management, AI-powered attendance tracking, analytics, and workflow automation into a unified cloud-native system.

The system uses facial recognition through Amazon Rekognition to enable contactless attendance marking. Employees can clock IN and OUT using a webcam interface, while administrators can monitor attendance, manage employees, approve leave requests, and analyze attendance patterns through an integrated dashboard.

The architecture is fully serverless and event-driven to ensure scalability, cost efficiency, and operational simplicity.

