# 8. AI Attendance Logic

## Rekognition Collection

### Collection Name

```text
employee-faces
```

### Matching Threshold

```text
95%
```

### Attendance Rules

| Condition        | Result   |
| ---------------- | -------- |
| First scan       | IN       |
| Second scan      | OUT      |
| Additional scans | Rejected |

